(179, 'Mareep', 55, 40, 40, 65, 45, 35, 'Wool Pokémon', 'Rubbing its fleece generates electricity. You’ll want to pet it because it’s cute, but if you use your bare hand, you’ll get a painful shock.', '0.6 m', '7.8 kg', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Purukitto/pokemon-data.json/master/images/pokedex/sprites/179.png', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Purukitto/pokemon-data.json/master/images/pokedex/thumbnails/179.png', 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Purukitto/pokemon-data.json/master/images/pokedex/hires/179.png', 2),
